overview.en: VNST(VNS Token).VNS is the first eco-platform project that fully integrates the AMT value concept after the AMT community has accumulated many years of ideas. The concept of VNS is closely related to the thinking of AMT community values, which can be said to be the crystallization of the AMT community. Because of the consensus of “creating value, transmitting value, and realizing value interconnection”, a group of AMT community members from different industries and regions come together to contribute to self-worth in order to achieve common goals. At present, the AMT community has built the first value-interconnect ecological platform, VNS. The VNS platform will carry the AMT community concept and bring together global value creators to provide comprehensive support and services for each ecological participant of VNS to help the flow of ecological values. To achieve mutual benefit and common growth for ecological participants.
overview.zh: VNST(VNS Token)。VNS是AMT社区在经历多年的理念沉淀后，充分融合了AMT价值理念的第一个生态平台项目。VNS的理念内涵与AMT社区价值思考息息相关，可以说是AMT社区的思想结晶。因为“创造价值、传递价值、实现价值互联”的共识,让一群来自不同行业、地区的AMT社区成员走到一起，为了实现共同的目标而贡献自我价值。目前AMT社区已经打造出第一个价值互联生态平台——VNS，VNS平台将承载AMT社区理念，汇聚全球价值创造者，为VNS每个生态参与者提供全面的支持与服务，助力生态价值的流动，实现生态参与者互惠共赢、共同成长。
